01:20:19,948 --> 01:20:22,280
With her friends.

507
01:20:22,450 --> 01:20:24,350
Ready or not, here I come.

508
01:20:26,388 --> 01:20:30,449
She made us promise
to stay upstairs.

509
01:20:40,602 --> 01:20:41,762
I was hiding.

510
01:21:00,622 --> 01:21:05,252
I was so scared, Rosie.
I didn't know what to do.

511
01:21:06,194 --> 01:21:09,595
You guys have to help me.
Okay? I'll do anything.

512
01:21:10,198 --> 01:21:13,429
I'll kill you! I'll kill you!

513
01:21:16,071 --> 01:21:17,732
Fuck it, I'm not going down for this.

514
01:21:17,906 --> 01:21:21,273
Shut up! No one's going down for this.
Sit down.

515
01:21:22,811 --> 01:21:25,143
It's gonna be okay.

516
01:21:25,747 --> 01:21:28,875
My dad,
he can take care of all of this.

517
01:21:31,820 --> 01:21:34,550
We need to do something now.

518
01:21:35,590 --> 01:21:37,785
- We'll keep it a secret.
- Where's Claire?

519
01:23:26,201 --> 01:23:29,329
I'm so sorry, Rose.

520
01:23:37,012 --> 01:23:38,741
Rose.

521
01:24:26,995 --> 01:24:28,963
Do you remember this?
Do you want it?

522
01:24:30,999 --> 01:24:31,988
Do you want it?

523
01:24:36,971 --> 01:24:38,700
No!

524
01:24:54,255 --> 01:24:55,279
Give her to me!

525
01:24:55,957 --> 01:25:00,155
You can't have her! Not this time!

526
01:25:06,434 --> 01:25:09,130
Claire! It's the door.

527
01:25:09,604 --> 01:25:12,698
The door is the port.
Break the glass.

528
01:25:13,641 --> 01:25:14,869
Break the door!

529
01:25:15,343 --> 01:25:17,811
Smash it! Hey!

530
01:25:19,147 --> 01:25:22,810
Hey, you come over here.
Come over here.

531
01:25:43,304 --> 01:25:46,865
Help! Help me!

532
01:25:57,619 --> 01:25:59,348
Hunt!

533
01:25:59,521 --> 01:26:02,251
- Throw me the blanket!
- Lead him to the door!

534
01:26:02,857 --> 01:26:04,347
To the door, Claire!

535
01:26:08,596 --> 01:26:10,530
Brendan!

536
01:28:21,162 --> 01:28:22,925
Bury it.

537
01:28:24,432 --> 01:28:26,423
Someplace dry.

538
01:28:31,806 --> 01:28:33,603
Thank you.

